  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a bento box or toaster oven to 375°F (190°C).\n Toast the Norwegian bread slices until lightly browned.\n Spread dairy-free butter on each slice.\n Top with fresh basil leaves and salt.\n Optional: sprinkle with sesame seeds, chopped nuts, dried fruit, cinnamon, or granola.\n Optional: drizzle with honey, maple syrup, or vanilla extract.\n Optional: sprinkle with coconut flakes, oats, or lemon zest.\n Optional: top with chopped banana or apple.\n Serve warm and enjoy!"
